接口说明
=============


接口需知
=============
1. 以 `ip2city.http` 为例
2. zk集群(参数zkidc)可选值说明::

    qa:  测试集群
    yz:  亦庄集群
    g1:  g1集群

3. 所有操作都是在 `/soa/services` 目录下
4. 返回值code为1表示请求成功，为0表示请求失败



[接口]查看服务列表
------------------------
url: servicelist/
类型: GET
参数::

    key
    zkidc

返回值::

    {code:1, services: [
        {service: <service>},
        {service: <service>}
    ]}

举例说明::

    {"code" : 1, "services" [
        {"service" : "ip2city.http"},
        {"service" : "idserver.thrift.http"}
    ]}


[接口]新增服务
-------------------
url: addservice/
类型: POST
参数::

    key:
    destName:
    zkidc:

返回值::

    {code: 1}


[接口]删除服务(需慎重)
--------------------------
url: delservice/
类型: POST
参数::

    key:
    destName:
    zkidc:

返回值::

    {code: 1}


[接口]查看指定服务的服务器列表
----------------------------------
url: serverlist/
类型: GET
参数::

    key
    destName:
    zkidc:

返回值::

    {code:1, servers: [
        {host: <host>, port:<port>, key: <key>}
    ]}

举例说明::

    {"code" : 1, "servers" : [
       {"host" : "192.168.1.1", "port" : 8080, "key" : "memeber_000000001"},
       {"host" : "192.168.1.2", "port" : 8080, "key" : "memeber_000000002"},
       {"host" : "192.168.1.3", "port" : 8080, "key" : "memeber_000000003"}
    ]}



[接口]给指定服务新增服务器
----------------------------
url: addserver/
类型: POST
参数::

    key:
    destName:
    zkidc:
    serverHost:
    serverPort:

返回值::

    {code: 1}


[接口]删除指定服务的服务器
----------------------------------
url: delserver/
类型: POST
参数::

    key:
    destName:
    zkidc:
    serverKey:

返回值::

    {code: 1}




错误返回值
----------------
::

    0: 失败
    {code: 0, reason: <reason>}

举例::

    
    {"code": 0, "reason": "interal server error!"}

    {"Code":0,"Reason":{"Value":"object","Type":{}}}


实例说明
---------------
::

    http://127.0.0.1:9090/servicelist?destName=hello&key=1122-3434&zkidc=qa

    http://127.0.0.1:9090/serverlist?destName=hello&key=1122-3434&zkidc=qa

    http://127.0.0.1:9090/addservice?destName=ip2city&keys=1122-3434&zkidc=qa

    http://127.0.0.1:9090/delservice?destName=ip2city&keys=1122-3434&zkidc=qa

    http://127.0.0.1:9090/addserver?destName=hello&keys=1122-3434&zkidc=qa&serverHost=127.0.0.1&serverPort=888

    http://127.0.0.1:9090/delserver?destName=hello&keys=1122-3434&zkidc=qa&serverKey=member_0000000013






